<br>
I always thought it was a pretty shitty thing to do. I'd personally ask the person before selling or getting rid of the item. (not like Tat wasn't on every single night of the week).<br>
<br>
He's in your guild. I wonder how many CiH would scream at me if I had put his name in the headlines in here. Guessing a lot -) Kinda crappy thats how it works.<br>
<br>
