Tatianae &quot;Who didn't used to think the flame CiH threads were cool, but dang you guys are always whining, getting ripped off, gated out on yadda yadda yadda&quot; Fatecaster <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/utatianaefatecaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tatianae Fatecaster</A> at: 6/12/01 4:03:09 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ubannion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bannion</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/9/01 1:54:18 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Thraxx the e-bay monk turned thief</span><hr size=1> Tat. I am a person, not a guild. I never posted on this board, much less any other flame board before today. I have meet you in game, helped you in game, ressed you in game. What is the deal? somone joins a guild you don't like, you auto hate them regardless how friendly they are to you in the past? What did I ever do you you but join a guild you don't like. Please don't be shallow. I have a legitmate complaint that you are using as a pesonal attack toward a guild you hate. that is a huge problem with people in this game is that they draw lines in the sand the moment you join a guild others do not like.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/uzenywutang.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeny WuTang</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/9/01 2:29:08 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Thraxx the e-bay monk turned thief</span><hr size=1> Bannion, I don't hate CiH, nothing close to it.<br>
