<br>
No? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/utatianaefatecaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tatianae Fatecaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 339<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/9/01 2:33:01 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ...</span><hr size=1> It is a fact people are scared to challenge you due to your guild hence the comment about your guild. Look at the Frizzy ordeal...posting in here solves nothing. It irritates me that it was in here..and they were left to defend themselves..because well I know what it feels like to have to defend ones self.  I am not saying I hate your whole guild but you guys have definately shown a trend of your values....<br>
