<br>
So I am going to stand up for Thraxx because damnit someone needs to. I will stand up for Frizzy, I will stand up for Phoenixx and I will stand up for myself.....anyone who is subjected to this type of &quot;screw them out of a good reputation- hence forcing them out of the game&quot; approach. <br>
<br>
I don't give a shit if &quot;your&quot; ancient cyclopse was KS'd mine was too once and I didn't have to come in here to cry about it. I don't give a dang if you were ripped off, your guild mate ripped me off and I didn't bring it in here. Countless others are subject to disagreement, misperceptions, actual malicious acts daily - unless they are &quot;all&quot; brought forth execution style &quot;none&quot; of them should be. And trust me if **every** misunderstanding in this game came out in this flame forum as xxxxx is guilty, there wouldn't be anyone left to PLAY THE DANG GAME! (Except for Cyanan because he's never been misunderstood hehe).<br>
<br>
